body_html:
@cxwx Can you open an issue at github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard with the following information:

  • What was the output that TensorBoard printed to console?
  • What was the output that TensorBoard printed to web console? (in chrome, right click on the page + click "inspect")
  • What browser are you using?
  • What OS are you using?
  • What exactly is TensorBoard displaying?

I'm closing this issue since this is the wrong place for TensorBoard issues.
